		"description": "# Dokumentasi API SIAKAD\n\n> **Status:** [PRODUCTION]  \n> **Version:** 1.0.0  \n> **Base URL:** `{{base_url}}`\n\n## ⚠️ PENTING - Cara Setup & Troubleshooting\n\n### 1️⃣ Setup Awal\n- Buka **Collection Variables** di tab kanan\n- Pastikan `base_url` = `http://localhost:8000/api` (dengan `/api`)\n- Jangan gunakan `http://localhost:8000` tanpa `/api`\n\n### 2️⃣ Headers Required\nSetiap request wajib punya headers:\n```\nContent-Type: application/json\nAccept: application/json\n```\n\n### 3️⃣ Troubleshooting: Jika Response HTML (Welcome Page)\n**MASALAH:** URL tidak punya `/api` prefix\n- ❌ Salah: `{{base_url}}/matakuliah/1` (jika base_url=localhost)\n- ✅ Benar: `http://localhost:8000/api/matakuliah/1`\n- ✅ Benar: `{{base_url}}/matakuliah/1` (jika base_url sudah include /api)\n\n**SOLUSI:** Cek dan update variable `base_url` ke: `http://localhost:8000/api`\n\n## Daftar Endpoint\nSetiap endpoint sudah siap digunakan.\nResponse mendukung JSON dan XML.",
